text:
This extension allows you to use font-awesome icons in your Quarto HTML and PDF documents. It provides an {{< fa >}} shortcode:

Mandatory <icon-name>:
{{< fa <icon-name> >}}
Optional <group>, <size=...>, and <title=...>:
{{< fa <group> <icon-name> <size=...> <title=...> >}}

For example: | Shortcode | Icon | | ————————————————– | —————————————– | | {{< fa thumbs-up >}} |  | | {{< fa folder >}} |  | | {{< fa chess-pawn >}} |  | | {{< fa brands bluetooth >}} |  | | {{< fa brands twitter size=2xl >}} (HTML only) |  | | {{< fa brands github size=5x >}} (HTML only) |  | | {{< fa battery-half size=Huge >}} |  | | {{< fa envelope title="An envelope" >}} |  |
